content: beanies with it too i have named the beanie the unley chill beanie as i have spent many wonderful years living in different parts of the unley city council area south australia it s a great place to live and bring up a family our #unleycrochetcrew made our first group charitable donation to the unley salvation army who have been actively serving the unley community for over 150 years by providing valuable services and programs i hope you enjoy making your unley chill beanie page | 8
